experiment_setup.paper_text:
We use the following simple templates to format the in-context examples. For SST-2, Subjectivity, Financial Phrasebank, Hate Speech, and our author identification task, we use the following line of Python code to format each input example: f"Sentence: {sentence} 
 Answer: {label}

".

goal_objective.paper_text:
Our goal is to develop a data-driven framework to accomplish the following:
(Pattern Recognition) identify the patterns and learn the recurrent structures P, and group segments into clusters according to their corresponding patterns p P;
(Pattern Generation) learn the distribution f( |p, α, β), p P;
(Pattern Evolution) learn the pattern transition probabilities Q(pj, αj, βj|pi, αi, βi).
